{"type":"article","id":10847,"title":"毛左激怒，浙江广厦俱乐部海报恶搞伟大领袖。。。","uid":3685,"topics":[3374,624,194,78,4217],"contents":"12月12日，CBA联赛浙江广厦官方微博发出一张赛前海报，引发争议。据悉，该海报将红太阳毛主席的形象修改为俱乐部吉祥物，有亵渎太祖之嫌，社会影响恶劣。当日，CBA公布相关处罚，俱乐部直接负责人终身禁止参加CBA联赛相关工作，球队被处罚100万元。浙江广厦发出道歉，称已开除海报除设计审核人员。<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ELlpFnQWkAEQMzh?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ELlpFnQWkAEQMzh?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ELlpFnQWkAEQMzh?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ELlpFnjX0AAmOfE?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ELlpFnjX0AAmOfE?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ELlpFnjX0AAmOfE?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ELlpFnRXsAAt1c7?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ELlpFnRXsAAt1c7?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ELlpFnRXsAAt1c7?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-12-12","agreeCount":4,"discussionCount":0}